parameters.name: EndpointName
parameters.description: The Redshift-managed VPC endpoint name. An endpoint name must contain 1-30 characters. Valid characters are A-Z, a-z, 0-9, and hyphen(-). The first character must be a letter. The name can't contain two consecutive hyphens or end with a hyphen.

parameters.name: SubnetGroupName
parameters.description: The subnet group from which Amazon Redshift chooses the subnet to deploy the endpoint.

parameters.name: VpcSecurityGroupIds
parameters.description: The security group that defines the ports, protocols, and sources for inbound traffic that you are authorizing into your endpoint. (string) ---
